{"tid":1322671,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"楊偉雄︰智慧燈柱收集交通等數據與私隱無關","createTime":"2019-07-16T04:14:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T04:27:38.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"38456019b1ee599c089e022714833a9e38028d9a","tid":1322671,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T04:14:22.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】政府正在各區分階段增設智慧燈柱。創新及科技局局長楊偉雄強調，燈柱主要收集交通、氣象數據，與個人私隱無關。<br />\n<br />\n楊偉雄︰「我們的數據是可以分享的數據，透明度高、開誠布公。我舉例空氣質素、氣象、交通情況等，資料全部可在政府一線通看到。現在某些數據與市民分享，市民很喜歡，完全與私隱無關。我們每行一步都有諮詢私隱專員公署，看看數據有否侵犯私隱。」"},{"pid":"10f234a340acfdf56d8a6d4c1e7eb9f922afadb8","tid":1322671,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T04:14:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=355571\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D355571&d=SZ2g%2FZg1uDubc4iNJejiXmmu51%2BDyw7Majob2ybULac%3D&h=4642f960\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D355571&h=dc4f0cef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=355571</a>"},{"pid":"e0bb613c27b6a9e4a240a38e8d1b3a5c6f92e9b7","tid":1322671,"uid":23707,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T04:15:08.000Z","msg":"OK我實信你啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b12ee0e4b7629bb4eca889c6193e71c4bee5d15","tid":1322671,"uid":50658,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T04:15:55.000Z","msg":"你出嚟消毒我就知方向又正確"},{"pid":"0fee6a6b5586dc3915e306745baed4e1bba00ade","tid":1322671,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T04:16:34.000Z","msg":"仲邊有人信你，個行騙長官都公然講大話，放啲濕碎嘢出嚟就以為呃到人咩屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"603ff71e9cc43887a6bb25afe47f7612316e879c","tid":1322671,"uid":137999,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T04:19:20.000Z","msg":"可以睇下Steve jobs有冇經過"},{"pid":"cbadda92868c3214500f5a7f6ee570e51a3857a1","tid":1322671,"uid":278765,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T04:27:38.000Z","msg":"智慧燈柱無可避免行過。但智能身份證/有smart chip信用卡。絕對可以阻止被閱讀，原始版本用錫紙包，現在有RFID shield /Faraday  銀包，卡套，背囊&hellip;&hellip;另外燈柱有冇咁大功率好得黎，size 又做到咁細，我唔敢講嘞！"}]}